~===============Euclid Elements Editions====================================
Two different translations are used
	1.	THE FIRST SIX BOOKS OF THE ELEMENTS OF EUCLID.
		BY JOHN CASEY.
	2.  EUCLID'S ELEMETS (THE THIRDTEEN BOOKS).
	    Translated BY THOMAS HEATH.
~		
~++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++Euclide: BOOK 1 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
								The Point.
JOHN CASEY:
	I. A point is that which has position but not dimensions.
THOMAS HEATH:
	1. A point is that which has no part.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------~ 
point has a position.
